name: Marmol #2
description:
Marmol #2 is part of a series of 4 images.

Marmol #2 was algorithmically generated with Python creating a random color with unknown seed.

The color of each pixel is calculated as an average of the color of the adjacent top and left pixels.

Then, again randomly, a value between -2 and 2 is added to each RGB component.

2048 x 2048 px.
